---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Projects"
  description="Explore all open source Java projects by Fugerit Coding Org — core libraries, tools and documentation."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="badge">Open Source</span>
      <h1>Projects</h1>
      <p>The complete ecosystem of Java libraries and frameworks maintained by Fugerit Coding Org.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- CORE LIBRARIES -->
      <div class="proj-category" id="core-libraries">
        <div class="proj-category__header">
          <h2>1. Core Libraries</h2>
          <p>The four foundational multi-module Maven projects that form the Fugerit ecosystem.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="proj-list">
          <article class="proj-item card" id="project-fj-bom">
            <div class="proj-item__meta">
              <span class="proj-num">1.0</span>
              <div>
                <h3><a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-bom" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">fj-bom</a></h3>
                <p class="proj-item__subtitle">BOM Parent POM</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>The parent POM providing common resources, dependency management and consistent build behaviours across all Fugerit projects. The foundation every other library inherits from.</p>
            <div class="proj-item__tags">
              <span class="badge">Maven</span>
              <span class="badge">BOM</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proj-item__links">
              <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-bom" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-bom-btn">GitHub ↗</a>
              <a href="https://central.sonatype.com/artifact/org.fugerit.java/fj-bom" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-bom-maven-btn">Maven Central ↗</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="proj-item card" id="project-fj-lib">
            <div class="proj-item__meta">
              <span class="proj-num">1.1</span>
              <div>
                <h3><a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-lib" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">fj-lib — Jupiter</a></h3>
                <p class="proj-item__subtitle">Core Java Utility Library</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>A comprehensive utility library covering configuration loading, IO operations, i18n, logging abstractions and common language primitives. Java 8 compatible with minimal external dependencies (only Apache Commons DBCP2 as optional).</p>
            <div class="proj-item__tags">
              <span class="badge">Java 8+</span>
              <span class="badge">IO</span>
              <span class="badge">i18n</span>
              <span class="badge">Config</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proj-item__links">
              <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-lib" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-lib-btn">GitHub ↗</a>
              <a href="https://central.sonatype.com/artifact/org.fugerit.java/fj-core" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-lib-maven-btn">Maven Central ↗</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="proj-item card" id="project-fj-doc">
            <div class="proj-item__meta">
              <span class="proj-num">1.2</span>
              <div>
                <h3><a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-doc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">fj-doc — Venus ⭐ 29</a></h3>
                <p class="proj-item__subtitle">Document Generation Framework</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>A powerful, modular document generation framework. Define documents in a neutral format and render them to PDF (Apache FOP), XLSX (Apache POI), HTML, DOCX, and more. Integrates with Freemarker for dynamic templating. Works seamlessly with Spring Boot, Quarkus and WebSphere Liberty.</p>
            <div class="proj-item__tags">
              <span class="badge">PDF</span>
              <span class="badge">XLSX</span>
              <span class="badge">HTML</span>
              <span class="badge">Freemarker</span>
              <span class="badge">Spring Boot</span>
              <span class="badge">Quarkus</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proj-item__links">
              <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-doc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-doc-btn">GitHub ↗</a>
              <a href="https://central.sonatype.com/artifact/org.fugerit.java/fj-doc-base" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-doc-maven-btn">Maven Central ↗</a>
              <a href="https://venusguides.fugerit.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-doc-guide-btn">Guides ↗</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="proj-item card" id="project-fj-daogen">
            <div class="proj-item__meta">
              <span class="proj-num">1.3</span>
              <div>
                <h3><a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-daogen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">fj-daogen — Mars</a></h3>
                <p class="proj-item__subtitle">Java Data Access Code Generation</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>A code generation library for creating entity beans and data access layers. Supports pluggable generators for different persistence strategies. While a simple persistence layer is included out of the box, custom generators can be added for any behaviour.</p>
            <div class="proj-item__tags">
              <span class="badge">Codegen</span>
              <span class="badge">DAO</span>
              <span class="badge">Entities</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proj-item__links">
              <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-daogen" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-daogen-page-btn">GitHub ↗</a>
              <a href="https://central.sonatype.com/artifact/org.fugerit.java/fj-daogen-base" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-daogen-maven-btn">Maven Central ↗</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="proj-item card" id="project-fj-universe">
            <div class="proj-item__meta">
              <span class="proj-num">1.4</span>
              <div>
                <h3><a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-universe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">fj-universe — Universe</a></h3>
                <p class="proj-item__subtitle">Ecosystem BOM</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>A unified Bill of Materials covering all Fugerit dependencies. Import <code>fj-universe</code> in your Maven project to manage the entire Fugerit ecosystem with a single, version-consistent dependency declaration.</p>
            <div class="proj-item__tags">
              <span class="badge">BOM</span>
              <span class="badge">Dependency Management</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proj-item__links">
              <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-universe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-universe-page-btn">GitHub ↗</a>
              <a href="https://central.sonatype.com/artifact/org.fugerit.java.universe/fj-universe" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="fj-universe-maven-btn">Maven Central ↗</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- GUIDES & QUICKSTARTS -->
      <div class="proj-category" id="documentation">
        <div class="proj-category__header">
          <h2>3. Documentation &amp; Quickstarts</h2>
          <p>Sample projects and guides to get started quickly with the Fugerit libraries.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="proj-list">
          <article class="proj-item card" id="project-fj-doc-guides">
            <div class="proj-item__meta">
              <span class="proj-num">3.1</span>
              <div>
                <h3><a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-doc-guides" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Venus Guides</a></h3>
                <p class="proj-item__subtitle">fj-doc Learning Resources</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>A collection of guides and tutorials for the Venus (fj-doc) library, including the classic Hello World PDF example and progressively advanced topics.</p>
            <div class="proj-item__links">
              <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-doc-guides" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="venus-guides-btn">GitHub ↗</a>
              <a href="https://venusguides.fugerit.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-ghost" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="venus-guides-site-btn">venusguides.fugerit.org ↗</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="proj-item card" id="project-fj-doc-quickstart">
            <div class="proj-item__meta">
              <span class="proj-num">3.2</span>
              <div>
                <h3><a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-doc-quickstart" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Venus Quickstart</a></h3>
                <p class="proj-item__subtitle">Ready-to-run Examples</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Runnable quickstart examples covering static documents, dynamic Freemarker-powered documents, and REST integration with Spring Boot, Quarkus, and WebSphere Liberty.</p>
            <div class="proj-item__links">
              <a href="https://github.com/fugerit-org/fj-doc-quickstart" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="font-size:0.85rem;" id="venus-quickstart-btn">GitHub ↗</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 9rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--gradient-hero);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--clr-border);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .page-hero .badge { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--clr-white); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .page-hero p { font-size: 1.05rem; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .proj-category { margin-bottom: 4rem; }
  .proj-category__header { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .proj-category__header h2 { color: var(--clr-white); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }

  .proj-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }

  .proj-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }

  .proj-item__meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .proj-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--clr-accent);
    background: rgba(0,168,150,0.12);
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .proj-item__meta h3 { font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--clr-white); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
  .proj-item__meta h3 a { color: inherit; }
  .proj-item__meta h3 a:hover { color: var(--clr-accent); }
  .proj-item__subtitle { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--clr-text-dim); }

  .proj-item__tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.4rem; }

  .proj-item__links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; margin-top: 0.25rem; }

  .proj-item p { font-size: 0.92rem; }

  .proj-item code {
    background: rgba(0,168,150,0.1);
    color: var(--clr-accent);
    padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }
</style>
